Chablis Baldwin-Natsume

  • daughter of Soseki Natsume and James Baldwin (OC)
    • youngest child of her family
  • girl, trans
    • she/her
  • lesbian
  • starts the series at 14 and ends at 21
  • born March 11th, 2000
  • Namesake: The Lady Chablis
  • Ability: Midnight in the Garden of Good and Evil
  • Affiliation: her main affiliation is with the Messenger Club, but she is also very much involved with the Gunslinger Kids and both the Apprentices of the ADA and the ADA itself. She is considered a friend to essentially all of the Gifted groups within Yokohama, and not just because of her father Natsume's influence
  • Level at which I think about them: high
  • Brief Notes:
    • Being the youngest of the Baldwin-Natsume family, and also their only girl, Chablis is definitely a little spoiled and extremely overprotected, but she does her best to be as humble as possible about it, and also prove to her family and friends that she's more than capable of handling her own business at times. Her older twin brother, Takehiro Baldwin-Natsume, is especially annoying when it comes to the overprotectiveness. Of her extended family, she is the closest to Junichi Fukuzawa, and not just in age; they've gotten along as friends ever since the two of them were barely toddlers.
